The paper discusses plagiarism in mathematical publications, which is a topic that falls under digital libraries (cs.DL) and computer security and cryptography (cs.CR). The authors also mention investigating editorial notes, which suggests information retrieval (cs.IR) as a possible sub-category. Additionally, the evaluation of plagiarism detection systems could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or software engineering (cs.SE).
